# Team Ownership and Review Requirements

# Backend team owns all server-side code
backend/ @your-team-backend
backend/app/ @your-team-backend
backend/ai/ @your-team-ml

# Frontend team owns UI and client-side code
frontend/ @your-team-frontend
frontend/src/ @your-team-frontend

# ML team owns AI models, prompts, and evaluation
backend/ai/ @your-team-ml
backend/ai/engines/ @your-team-ml
backend/ai/models/ @your-team-ml
backend/ai/prompts/ @your-team-ml
datasets/ @your-team-ml

# DevOps/Infra owns deployment and CI/CD
.github/ @your-team-devops
docker-compose*.yml @your-team-devops
Dockerfile* @your-team-devops
Makefile @your-team-devops
vercel.json @your-team-devops

# Documentation team owns docs and runbooks
docs/ @your-team-docs
*.md @your-team-docs

# Default fallback for unowned files
* @your-team-lead